These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, cherry, tomato, pomegranate
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, puzzles, singing, video-games
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, vegafina, aristoff, havana
House: wooden, tower, cottage, townhouse
1. the vegafina-smoker is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is between the person eating tomato and the person eating pomegranate##2
3. the vegafina-smoker is the wooden house##1
4. the townhouse house is on the left of the wooden house##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
6. the cottage house is the person eating tomato##1
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
8. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
9. the person eating cherry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Food   | cherry | pomegranate   | orange  | tomato  |
| Hobby   | puzzles    | video-games    | filmmaking      | singing    |
| Cigar   | havana | vegafina | aristoff | prince |
| House     | townhouse  | wooden       | tower    | cottage     |

