.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
City: berlin, venice, prague, miami
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, cabbage, pineapple, spinach
4 different games are played: whist, backgammon, bridge, snooker
House: ranch-style, cottage, wooden, art-deco
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
3. the person playing snooker is the cottage house##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
5. the person eating spinach is between the person playing bridge and the ranch-style house##2
6. the art-deco house is between the person eating spinach and the person playing snooker##2
7. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
8. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
9. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| City         | miami | venice    | prague  | berlin    |
| Food   | strawberry      | cabbage  | spinach  | pineapple |
| Game           | snooker      | bridge       | backgammon      | whist       |
| House         | cottage    | art-deco | wooden | ranch-style |

