.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, emerald, lilac, white
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, go, snooker
4 different pets are kept: goat, turtle, ferret, cat
House: craftsman, victorian, palace, colonial
1. the owner of the ferret is the victorian house##1
2. the victorian house is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
3. the palace house is on the left of the victorian house##1
4. the victorian house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
5. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person playing go##1
6. the owner of the turtle is the person playing snooker##1
7. the person who likes white is on the right of the person playing go##1
8. the person who likes pink is between the person playing bridge and the person playing snooker##2
9. the person playing go is between the person who likes lilac and the owner of the turtle##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Color        | emerald | lilac     | pink   | white     |
| Game       | mah-jongg   | bridge   | go | snooker |
| Pet         | goat   | ferret | cat       | turtle    |
| House   | palace    | victorian | craftsman  | colonial    |

